Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.15,0:20:17.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.81,0:20:19.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽 你在看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.08,0:20:33.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那首歌 原本只是想傳達給家人的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.00,0:20:36.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連ARUS的人也收到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.63,0:20:38.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定也傳達到迪歐爾的人那了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.05,0:20:39.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.55,0:20:42.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 去向晴人道謝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.38,0:20:44.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晴人呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.80,0:20:45.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在探險隊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.47,0:20:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說要先把握清楚這顆Module
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.10,0:20:51.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.81,0:20:53.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一路順風
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.35,0:20:55.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你幫我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.35,0:20:57.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是說做記錄的事情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.27,0:21:00.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是說唱歌的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.73,0:21:02.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以為你會討厭那種事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.57,0:21:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.40,0:21:07.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我也很感激
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.41,0:21:12.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自從進了這座學校就已經放棄了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.51,0:21:30.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.26,0:21:32.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.90,0:21:47.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詛咒 還有其他的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.62,0:21:54.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像彩虹一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.04,0:21:55.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.04,0:22:03.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件事 能作為我們兩個人的秘密保密嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.63,0:22:09.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像我這樣的人 我不想再增加了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.89,0:22:17.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.73,0:22:22.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為交換 我們兩人一起吧
